name: Rabbit's Jetpack
description:
The white rabbit is tired of the jumping life and he takes a jetpack, flying towards the adventure.

But there is one problem: where to get so much fuel to fly to another island?

He has to save fuel and pick up bonuses in order to fly.

This game is an unusual runner with an endless world in which you will need to control a rabbit with just one button.

Do you think it's easy?

Let's see how you do it.
